   the beginning, their top priority was the availability of information
   bidirectionally between the control station and the remote units;
   however, the growing escalation of industrial systems, as well as
   internet connectivity has led to reconsider the old paradigm to give
   more importance to the issue of security, in order to avoid a possible
   cyber-attack endangers the functioning of the SCADA system. These
