   strategies are very sophisticated and rely on perfect system knowledge.
   The resulting attack signal is completely invisible in the sensor
   readings. Hence an ordinary fault diagnosis system is not able to detect
   such attacks and to trigger an alarm. Our goal is to insert a modulation
